headline: Medtronic BrainSense™ Adaptive Deep Brain Stimulation named a 2025 TIME Best Inventions
summary: Medtronic plc (NYSE: MDT), a global leader in healthcare technology, today announced that BrainSense™ Adaptive Deep Brain Stimulation (aDBS) – the world's first closed-loop DBS system for people with Parkinson's – has been recognized by TIME on its annual list of Best Inventions.
